        Subnets configuration for the target VPC.
        The format of subnet name should be follow the name prefix of \"fgt_login_\", \"fgt_internal_\", \"tgw_attachment_\", \"gwlbe_\", "ngw_", \"privatelink_\". Specify the target subnet you needed.
